<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνωνι χαίρειν Ἁρμάεις καὶ Τεῶς. ἐνέβημεν εἰς τὰ ἔργα ἀπὸ <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="34">λδ</num>, σοῦ 

    <lb n="2"/>συντάξαντος ἡμῖν τοῖς ἔργοις προσέχειν τετράμηνον. ἔστιν δὲ ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="3"/>μῆνες ἑκκαίδεκα <choice><corr>ἀφ᾽</corr><sic>απ</sic></choice> οὗτε <choice><corr>παρεστήκαμεν</corr><sic>παραστηκαμεν</sic></choice> τοῖς ἔργοις μετὰ Ὥρου τοῦ σοῦ 

    <lb n="4"/>ὑπηρέτου· καὶ ἀναπληροῦν ἡμᾶς ποιεῖ ὃ ἂν λάβωμεν καὶ ὃ ἂν οἱ ξένοι λάβωσει. 

    <lb n="5"/>ἔστιν δὲ ὃ διδόασιν ἡμῖν παρὰ τὰς μυρίας <num value="10000"/> πεντακοσίαν <num value="500"/>, καὶ ταῦτα προσεισ-

    <lb n="6"/>πράσσει ἡμᾶς. καλῶς ἂν οὖν ποιήσαις ἐπισκεψάμενος ἡμᾶς καὶ μὴ <choice><corr>περιιδεῖν</corr><sic>περιειδειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="7"/>παραπολλυμένους τῆι λειμῶι, ἀνακαλεσάμενος Ὧρον διαλογίσεσθαι 

    <lb n="8"/>ἡμῖν.  <space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>   εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.935" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.935" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notBefore="-0251-05-21" type="textDate">nach 21. Mai 251 v.Chr. (Jahr unsicher)</date></p></div><div n="meta.935" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Datierung nach dem Ende des 34. makedonischen Regierungsjahrs.</p></div><div n="meta.935" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59291</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">935</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59291</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;2;59291" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.935" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.935" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="fr"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl default="NO" type="translations">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 127</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.935" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" full="yes" type="ancientFindspot">Philadelphia</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" full="yes" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>), 